  "summary": "Hashicorp Nomad ACLs Cannot Deny Access to Workload\u2019s Own Variables",
  "details": "A vulnerability was identified in Nomad and Nomad Enterprise (\u201cNomad\u201d) such that a deny ACL capability could not be applied to a workload\u2019s own variables. If included, the Nomad ACL system will silently fail to block access. This vulnerability, CVE-2023-1296, was fixed in Nomad 1.4.6 and 1.5.1.",
